Citation.sTitle: Measurement and Correlation of the Liquid Density and Viscosity of HFO-1336mzz(Z) (cis-1,1,1,4,4,4-Hexafluoro-2-butene) at High Pressure
Citation.sAbstract: This work reported experimental measurements of the density and viscosity of cis-1,1,1,4,4,4-hexafluoro-2-butene (HFO-1336mzz(Z)) over wide ranges of temperature
